title: クイーン PV特集
detail:
4月17日(1975年)に初めて日本に降り立ち「クイーンの日」と認定された事を記念して、クイーンのミュージックビデオ特集をオンエア！
◇▼プレイリスト
【クイーン MUSIC VIDEO SPECIAL】
WE ARE THE CHAMPIONS
KILLER QUEEN
SOMEBODY TO LOVE
YOU'RE MY BEST FRIEND
BOHEMIAN RHAPSODY
BICYCLE RACE
FAT BOTTOMED GIRLS
ANOTHER ONE BITES THE DUST
PLAY THE GAME
FLASH
SAVE ME
DON'T STOP ME NOW
CRAZY LITTLE THING CALLED LOVE
WE WILL ROCK YOU
I WANT TO BREAK FREE
UNDER PRESSURE
HAMMER TO FALLRADIO GA GA
A KIND OF MAGIC
ONE VISION
I WANT IT ALL
THE SHOW MUST GO ON
INNUENDO
HEAVEN FOR EVERYONE
I WAS BORN TO LOVE YOU (2004 Video)
LET ME IN YOUR HEART AGAIN
WE WILL ROCK YOU (FAST) from「LIVE AT THE FORUM, MONTREAL 1981」
ANOTHER ONE BITES THE DUST from「LIVE AT THE FORUM, MONTREAL 1981」
WE ARE THE CHAMPIONS from「LIVE AT THE FORUM, MONTREAL 1981」

※オンエア楽曲は予告なく変更になる場合がございます
